* Create Procedures\nfor Multi-step Operations
** SQL stored procedures
***_ Sequences of SQL statements
***_ Variables, control flow, error handling
** CREATE PROCEDURE statement
***_ Requires Runtime 17.0+
***_ Currently in preview
** Parameter types
***_ IN: input parameters
***_ OUT: output parameters
***_ INOUT: both
** SQL SECURITY INVOKER
***_ Runs with caller's permissions
** Execute with CALL statement
***_ CALL catalog.schema.procedure(args)
